reviews.review_text: Might as Well ends the first set It's mistakenly listed as the set 2 opener. First one in like two years or something. Smokin' great show. Eyes> Foolish brings the house down. Wonderful first set too.

Long Lost "Memories" was there all 3 nights @ the crap centre and "remember" this blowing the other 2 nights away but just listening to this show for the 1st time since that night. 

Wish the 2nd set never ended!
the dead was smokin @ the cap centre this is grateful dead @ its finest post brent! the 2nd set is off the hook. thanks charlie miller
Happy Anniversary! Sounds great - thx Charlie as usual!!!
